ading-relaxed","children":"ISO 41001 is an international standard that specifies the requirements of Facility Management(FM). It follows the same structure as ISO 45001, ISO 50001. ISO 41001 standard helps the organizations to follow the facility management efficiently and effectively and meet the requirements of ISO 41001 facility management."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":"ISO 41001:2018 Standard is non-specific to any industry and intended to be applicable to all types of organizations and the scope of facility management must be defined. ISO 41001 Facility Management System is relevant to build a sustainable infrastructure that helps in enhancing the employee productivity and growth of the business."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"ISO 41001 Facility Management"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 mb-4","children":"Facility management consists of multiple disciplines that influence the efficiency and productivity of organizations. ISO standard for facility management determines the quality of life in societies through the services it manages and delivers. ISO 41001 facility management has a broad impact on the society and organization, but there is limited recognition of its principles and practices."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700","children":"ISO 41001:2018 Certification offers a perfect solution for organizations to achieve business growth. The requirement of ISO 41001 Facility Management System defines a common global structure and support system for an organization."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"Get Certified with ISO 41001:2018 Standard"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 mb-4","children":["$L4"," for an organization in the field of organizational infrastructural developments. Facility Management Standard helps the organization to be on top of the ever-changing trends. Considering the operations, and maintenance of the organization, the services of facility management must be constantly improved."]}],"$L5"]}],"$L6","$L7","$L8","$L9"]}]}],"$La"]}]}]]}],"$Lb","$Lc"],["$Ld"],"$Le"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
